{
  "texts": [
    "The results in Table 6 show that two-layer architectures have been better than single-layer architectures.",
    "Also, they have been more successful in finding the pattern and the relationship of different features.",
    "The method of \"attention\" is derived from human visual attention.",
    "Just as man focuses on certain parts of visual inputs for cognition or perception.",
    "Integrating the \"attention\" technique with Rnns helps to process long and noisy inputs."
  ]
}